high_descs: Go forward to the table, turn left, go forward to the counter.
Take the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn right, go forward to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave. Take the mug from the microwave.
Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn right.
Put the mug back in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Walk up to the kitchen island, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the coffee mug that is on the coffee machine on the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the coffee mug inside then close the door, turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave and remove the coffee mug then close the door.
Turn around and walk back over to the coffee machine.
Put the heated coffee mug into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated coffee mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Walk to the coffee maker on your left.
Pick up the mug from the maker.
Walk to the microwave on your right.
Put the mug in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the coffee maker.
Put the cup back in the maker.
anns.task_desc: Warm a mug for making coffee.
